content.detailedDescription:
I was going through videos and found this. we had a small kodak camera that was water proof and was like a phone we carried everywhere. our 4 year old loved to play with it. he unskillfully at times videoing videoing outside at a b-day party. there were tornado warnings and so we were standing looking at the clouds. he said to me, "dad i see lights in the sky and pointed" the way he said it was odd. instinctively i didn't doubt asking for the camera and started filming where he pointed. i didn't see anything as i looked and turned on the camera. i videoed a couple shots placating to him at this point and asking him to tell us what he saw. he can be heard in the video. 

tonight while moving our family videos over to the new computer i ran across three videos. but only recalled two i shot. the first in the series blew me away. there they were. he had caught them and was trying to tell me and i didn't ever check if he had actually filmed something assuming it not remotely possible. 

so all this time i thought he was pulling our leg. we have so many videos that i haven't began to watch 20% of them. i just film and download then say i will one day get around to doing something with them.

in a way, i am kind of glad i didn't see it till now because he wouldn't been able to understand what was going on, besides how would i explain  it to him. i just found them and im going to talk to his mom on what tyo say. 

im really blown away. i couldn't sleep so i just had to share it. i just really cant believe he caught them on video. i would take a lie detector to this story and videos. so you tell me what he saw!!!

content.detailedDescription: I really can't even explain what i saw. completely amazing. we were coming out of the luxor (my dad and i), and we started looking up at the beam that the luxor emits. there was a star like object that first moved into the beam, out of the beam, into the beam, then shot off like a shooting star. about 15 seconds later, it reappeared and did the same thing, then about 30 seconds later did the same thing again. 3 times it appeared and disappeared. completely mind shattering. my first ufo experience.
content.summary: Disappeared 3 times. made movements i have never seen before. an event that challenges everything i believe in.

content.detailedDescription: I was in my room playing on my phone. throughout the evening i had periodically looked out the window to see the stars, i was about to do this again and something in the night sky caught my eye. at first i thought it was a plane, because a flight path goes right next to my property, but the "plane" didn't have the same light patterns as this object did. the object had a constant bright warm whitish light coming from it. at first it seemed like it was hovering,but then it started to move. i opened my window and stuck my head out to see if it made a noise, it did not. i thought, as the bright object moved closer to the train tracks, my friends property, and my property to get it on video. it took me maybe ten seconds to take my phone off the charger and put it on video, but when i looked up again, the btight object had just vanished. i immediately told my parents, then for the rest of the night (till about 22:00) i stayed up hoping to see something that even resembled what i saw, nothing showed. my parents told me they saw the same thing two weeks ago, that was considerably lower in elevation and towards a different spot next to our property, with no explanation of what it was. plus there has been more "ufo" sightings (approximately 10) in my area.
content.summary: A very bright light appearing, moving, then vanishing.

On 1-7-16, 6:30pm went outside to see five star display high in eastern sky with one variation, instead of four guardian like craft following the five star display, there is only two. two, flashing red, blue, green and white. i notice in the western sky, one guardian like craft, flashing red, blue, green and white. 7:45pm the guarding in the western sky is gone. the five star and two guarding's in the eastern sky, seen same as on every clear night. every clear night the five star display comes in from the east, stops short of hwy 174, then slowly ascends into outer space, with two guardians following.
1-10-16, 9pm it's very cold outside, but the skies clear, five star display with two guarding's in eastern sky same as always. i'll only report this again if it makes any changes. it's  useless to report something that's here every night, yet remains not to be recorded as a star system. it seems no one cares.
content.summary: What i call guardians coming behind five star display

content.detailedDescription: I was in the back yard cleaning up a little until it started to get dark.I was about to head into the house until i noticed how nice and clear the it was,i started looking at the stars for a good minute or so and i was thinking about going into the house because my mother gave me a map of the stars but as soon as i was about to go in this star like object started cruising from ne to sw at a consistant speed with no noise and no trail or streak behind it.I have seen many falling stars and that is not what this was,i watched it stay at the same altitude until it was out of sight behind the tall evergreen trees which is were i saw some light through the trees and i went in because i got a little spooked because i saw this once before and i tried to blow that one off as an airplane but this reaffirmed what i saw.
content.summary: I saw a star like ufo

content.detailedDescription:
Northwest oklahoma city, oklahoma
on monday, january 4, 2016, i woke up at my usual time, 5:30am, to let the dogs out in the backyard. as i stood on my back porch, waiting for my dogs, i noticed a bright light in the dark sky. the light was white, with no tint of yellow. at first sight, the light appeared as a disc-shaped object. unsure what i was looking at, i quickly went inside to get my husband's phone, which has a better zoom feature than the camera on my phone. i went back outside, and the glowing object had changed from a disc shape to a circle, however, seemed to have the same diameter. the size was not remarkably different. i took notice of the tree branches below the object, within my field of vision, which seemed to be a great distance from the object. i memorized the branches in relation to the object in order to measure any changes in the object's potential movement. the moon was visible some distance above the object, from my visual perspective. tiny stars were scattered throughout the sky, only visible as pinpricks at this hour. i used my husband's cell phone camera/video recorder to zoom in on the object. the object consisted of a circle of connected, white light, with a smaller circle of light inside. the small circle of light pulsated to and from the outer circle. having memorized the tree branches and other landmarks within my view, i am sure that the object itself did not move in the sky. it remained in the same spot, where i continued to watch it for approximately one hour. at one point, an airplane flew across the sky, below the object. the object still did not move. every once in a while, it looked as if the light emitted by the object would change colors, but not so clearly that one color could be named. the light itself would warp, similar to the fuzzy light changes of a broken tv channel. the object itself never once traveled. after taking several pictures and two videos, i returned inside. i got ready for work and went back outside around 7:00am. the object had disappeared. i watched the videos i took closely. in one video, i can hear a train sounding its horn, and the object seems to respond to the sound by a warping of shape/light for a brief moment. the object itself never once travels/moves from its original position in the sky.
content.summary: Circle of connected light remains stationary for at least one hour

content.detailedDescription: Since my childhood i have always observed the sky with fascination. i liked it a lot especially in vacations, outside of town,  at my grandfather's farm, where there was no artificial lighting close during sleep time at night. included i even wanted to be an astronomer. being walking to my house in december 2007, in the approximate date and time indicated, watching the sky i saw a bright and flaming object without tail at a considerable speed. when i saw it, it changes of direction abruptly and totally opposite of it flight path. i stayed watching the object until it is lost on the horizon. i have seen things far superior in my life and that many few people have or have had that responsability or possibility to see. i had not mentioned it before because i have analyzed the fact or situation. until recently i saw a program on history channel 2 (h2) where mentioned to you and since then i wanted to share that moment with emotion with peolple who had had similar experiences in this particular aspect. i have concluded that the purpose of them is to get something that does not have (and i believe know that it is), because the goal of a researcher or a visitor is known, in any case, look into a knowledge that does not have or need or your state or situation.
content.summary: I saw a flaming object at a considerable speed in the sky and abruptly changing of direction

content.detailedDescription: I was working on a school project with my daughter when i let the dogs out back. i looked up and saw what looked like the mythical "donuts on a rope" contrail to the west. i called my daughter to come look as we have talked about the aurora project possibility in the past and wanted her to see the very unique contrail. i have seen several contrails over central texas like this and one other time watched and object moving at an extreme high rate of speed across the sky. just as i was turning to go back into the house i saw an object to the east of the contrail moving at an extremely high rate of speed. this time i grabbed my phone and got a shot of it. the object was at an extreme altitude and no noise was evident. due to the perceived altitude i was able to assume it was traveling at an exceptional rate of speed. it traversed the sky from right to left (east to west in just seconds. the sun was very bright and i could not see if my screen was picking up the event. i backed into the house and caught the last several seconds of the flight on the highest magnification. even with that, it's impossible to make out the object.
content.summary: Possible procect aurora sighting. donuts on a rope contrail and very high speed object

content.detailedDescription: I was coming home from work about 5:20 pm. i turned onto my street and something caught my eye to the se. it had just turned dark so i could not make much detail. the craft was large and made no noise. it continued to come towards me at not too high an altitude. it went over all the houses on my street and over me as well. it was a triangle shaped craft. it had circular rows of distinctive red lights on the underside with a few white lights towards the center. toward the rear there some white tubular lights running the width of the craft. there was a white light in the rear that flashed every 2 seconds or so. you could see this light when the craft was directly over me but as the craft passed and was in the horizon the light was in the configuration of a figure eight with the corners rounded. the tubular light was constant and flashed brighter every 2 seconds. it disappeared just to the left of song mountain (with the ski area) probably going over the town of vespar to the ne.What struck me most was the slow speed of the craft and the distinctive figure eight of the tail light which i estimate was over 250 feet in width and 75 feet in height.
content.summary: Coming home. turned unto street. saw something in sky to se. stoped, got out and observed.

content.detailedDescription: Estavamos a comemorar o natal, por volta das 23 horas, ha volta de uma fogueira, quando reparamos que a lua estava mais luminosa e tinha uma aura que nunca tinha visto... achando que captava, tiramos uma foto com a camera digital. mas essa aura não aparece na foto, mas sim, dois objectos estranhos parecendo umas esferas que refletem a luz! vejam a foto e ampliem a mesma, que poderam constatar isso.
content.summary: Estavamos a ver uma aura anormal da lua, e tiramos uma foto, nessa  aparecem objetos com volume e a grande altitude!

content.detailedDescription: We were driving home at about 6:30 pm jan 6th 2016. got to our street and first spotted one large yellow orb over lake st. clair flying west towards us. pulled over to see what it was doing, but then it made an abrupt turn towards the south and disappeared. turned around and noticed two more large wide glowing (almost like yellow flames) in the nnw hovering and then dropping down slowly to just above the tree line, seemed about a mile away. getting closer they appeared saucer shaped (wider than tall but with no discernible dome) and were strobing red & white horizontally. they stayed fairly low and started slowly moving southwest (crossing the street we were driving on [this is when we got the best view]) but we couldn't catch up to them. they were getting smaller and farther away towards the sw. two more orbs appeared in the original nnw direction but were faint and star like. decided to turn back because we were tired and we saw a flashing orb (it almost looked like it was rotating) approaching from the south sitting at a traffic light. this is when i told my passenger to please take my phone and get a picture, but she didn't know how to zoom in. i poked my head over to watch it. it was an icy blue metallic color and round and it passed almost directly overhead. it flashed a few times and was very eerie looking and then my passenger saw it momentarily zip extremely fast across to another point in the sky.  we couldn't track it anymore as it had disappeared out of our view from the car once we started moving. we saw two more approaching white orbs on the way back in the east over the lake. i only have the one picture of the blue things approach, and it really looks nothing like what we saw with our eyes. it's the little dot way up in the sky directly over the bus stop in the pic. extremely disappointing that this is all we could get but i'm going to submit it anyway.
content.flightPath: Hovering then path,Path with directional change
content.summary: Multiple orbs and two strobing discs in one night

content.detailedDescription:
My brother and i were lying on our backs in a clearing in the woods. we were listening to a cassette player and star gazing. suddenly a bright white light flew into view. it was approximately the size of my thumbnail held at arms length. neither of us said a word. the light suddenly stopped still. then it zigzagged 45 degrees to the right and stopped again. then it continued it's original course. then it zigzagged again and stopped still.Still neither of had said a word. the object flew away on it's original course and disappeared over the tree tops. 

i was the first to speak and i said frank (an alias)"did you see that?"
he said "yeah i did!"
i said"what did it do?"
he said" it went like that and then like that and now it's gone!
i forgot to mention that it zigzagged twice and came to a complete stop each time.

i watched the local newspaper and watch the local news(out of jackson, msfor several days afterward to see if anyone else had witnessed what we had. to no avail. we didn't mention the incident to our folks for many years. i am an air force veteran, i served from 1972 to 1976. my brother had spent 4 years in the air force and got out in 1985. 

my job in the military was classified secret since i worked on electronic countermeasures gear on b-52's and the f-4 phantom .Everyone at that time knew that the sr-71 was the fastest aircraft in the world. this object(if it had a crew) would have torn them to pieces with the g's that it pulled.

this sighting only lasted a few seconds, but it had an enormous impact on both of us!
content.summary: A white orb (well defined edges) passed overhead, then zigzagged 45 degrees to right. halted continued original course, then zigzagged 45 degrees to right again. stopped then returned to original course!

content.detailedDescription: It was the day before christmas eve. i was spending the holiday with my sister in orange county, california. early that morning i got up. my sister came out to talk before her kids woke up. we were sitting on the sofa at sunrise and out over a hill maybe 500 feet high, i saw the sunlight reflecting off of something curved. i pointed it out to my sister and she saw it too. it moved slowly over the hill eastward until it disappeared behind the hill. it was a large disc shape. it reflected the sunlight pretty sharply. otherwise it would have been invisible. the sunlight reflecting was revealing the shape of the object. crescent around the exterior. i live near an airport and see jets and military jets all the time. this was moving slow which made me think it was a very large object. at least as big as a passenger airliner.
content.summary: The disc shape was moving over a hill at sunrise. it would have been invisible if the sunlight hadn't been reflecting off of it.

A ufo was in the sky. then there were lights

content.detailedDescription: I was watching tv, when i looked outside, i saw what i thought was a star but i relized it was way too low and bright. i recoreded 17 seconds on my phone and i looked at it through binocluars, i diditn see a solid shape, but it was bright than it would almos lt fade out.  after bout 5 to 10 mins i started to watch tv again when i looked up a couple minutes later it was gone.        ive tried to attacth my recording to ur website. when i click attach files it lets me choose video recording but it wouldnt let me view my videos
content.summary: Saw a orb or something

content.detailedDescription: Shortly after july 4 1987 i was washing dishes at a late 2 am not unusual because i worked second shift at the factory.I noticed a bright sphere shaped object flying low altitude from the southwest.It flew in a circular path like a spiral at a good rate of speed exhibiting a nonballistic flight characteristic.Instantly excited i ran out front door to try to see object as it passed by.Looked northeast but didnt see object pass by.Looked around and saw object hovering over back yard.Rural location no street lights and completely  overcast.Watched object for about 5 minutes then ran in house to retrieve rifle with scope to view object.Looked through scope at object for several minutes.Sphere shaped object extremely bright light.Went to back yard to see better.Object didnt move at this point.Walked north to south under object to try and estimate how high it was from ground.Got on the other side of it quickly estimate object was hovering under 200 feet.Stood in yard staring at object with naked eye thinking i would like to see object more closely.Object then moved downward and toward me stopping and hovering around 20 feet from ground and about 50 feet from me.I had feelings of extreme excitement.Feeling i wanted to try and communicate with object i went to a windchime hanging on the edge of my duplex about 30 feet from object.I tried to mimick tones from close encounter movie on my wind chimes.After a few times was able to mimick the tone pattern and repeated it multiple times.Then i walked back toward object where i had been standing before.Object descended to about 10 feet and came closer to me about 20 feet away.Immediatly felt emotions of joy and elation.Object returned to previous position.No sound,no illumination of object on ground or surroundings yet bright enough to produce glare on my glasses lenses.Thought in my mind come closer i want to see you better.Again object immediatly came closer. slow descent same  path as before but got closer.Once again i was filled with feelings of elation.Object returned to previous position.I did a little dance and thoght come closer i want to see you up close.Object came within ten feet and more quickly this time.This time i felt overwhelmed and felt like i used to before i played a sporting event or went to the principals office,like butterfly stomach.Object returned about 20 feet off ground about 50 feet away.This repeated several times.Every time object came closer when about ten feet away from me i got overwhelmed with nervous anxiety.When i did object woul return to farther away position .Same flight path same position.Mosquitos were really bad and was without shoes or socks.Was getting bit badly and retreated to duplex for shoes and socks.Returned to back yard and i spotted object moving slowly away.Was over road about an eighth of a mile away.Thought in my mind for object to come back and immediatly it came back to same position above back yard.Thought in my mind come really close i want to know what you are.Object came closer than before iam 6 feet and it was even with my head and 5 or six feet distance from me.Extreme anxiety in my stomach to the point i could not take it.Object reacted immediatly and returned to distant position.Went through this a couple more times.Feeling wore out and overwhelmed i said goodbye did the chime tones again and went inside.Watched object slowly take a path over near road and moved away to the south.Looked at clock to check time about 2:30 am.Duration about 30 minutes.Went to bed exhausted.Woke up next day covered in mosquitoe bites but exhilerated from previous nights experience.Told my nieghbor about it laughed and seemed skeptical.The night after first incident went to bed around 10pm.Trying to sleep i kept hearing my windchimes dinging softly.Had bedroom window open hot humid and no air conditioner.Looked out at chimes no wind at all.Went back to bed a short time later heard chimes ding again this time louder and with the same pattern i had used the night before.Really scared me.Looked out saw nobody there and no wind thought neighbor might be pranking me.Laid back down and it happened again same pattern and loud.Felt scared and panicky.Put pants on and grabbed my pistol then ran around to back yard.Looked around and saw a figure standing near a friends dwelling illuminated in his back porch light.Clothing seemed odd with a very high collar.To much clothes for the heat and humidity of july.Could not see face or details of garments was to dark and shadowy.Felt agitated and said who are you what do you want.Figure just stayed there like it was staring at me.Thought my nieghbor might have put my frind up to spooking me as a joke so i approached the figure quickly.Figure turned and moved away from me to the east as i approached from the west.As it moved away in a line heading east about10 or 15 feet from the back of the back of the duplexes i quickened my pace to a trot.As i was catching up to figure it went past a window with its kitchen light on.Figure was similar highth as me around 6 feet tall and looked like it was wearing a high collar coat or robe.Figur moved out of window light and towards a large tree.I was agitated and said get out of here as i went past the lit window with my pistol extended in a firing position.I heard a gasp and turned to see my state trooper nieghbor drop her dishrag and plate into a sink full of water,iwas about 6feet away from her and could see by her facial expression and vocalization she was startled.I turned to see figure go behind a large tree and said i have got you now.When i went around tree trunk there was nothing there.I looked over to neighbor female state trooper and she was not in front of the sink and not in sight in the kitchen.Bewildered i went to my friends house where the back porch light was on went around front and  noticed through his window he and another of my friends visiting were asleep on sofa and a chair.Another nieghbor was working on his car in duplex next door and i asked if he had seen anyone walking around he said no.I walked on home expecting my state trooper nieghbor to call the sherriff or come see why i went past her kitchen window that late at night with a pistol saying get out of here.No one ever came over.I  didnt have a handgun permit and was worried i was in trouble.Didnt have a home phone to call anyone.Was really shook up by incident couldnt stop sweating almost shaking fear.Was trying to come to grips with what happened night before then this.Was really fearful went to bed later in fear.Two days later landlord knocked on my door and asked if i had seen state trooper she didnt go to work the previous day and no one could find her.Really sent a chill through me.I told my landlord what had occured on condition he didnt tell police.He was a coworker and honored my request.I did not want to be questioned about it for several reasons.The sherfiffs office knocked on the door and asked if i had seen her.State troopers ,local police and county deputies combed the surrounding countryside.The local paper ran a story on her disapearance.The larger news sources at the state capitol both tv and newspaper did stories about trying to find her.This was a state trooper and people were very concerned.My landlord knocked on my door on i think day 4 or 5 after her disapearance and said she was home.I asked what happened and  landlord said trooper woke up on the floor of her duplex with no recollection of what happened.I asked landlord to explain my experience of what i went through both nights prior to her disapearance to try to jog her memory.He came back and said she didnt want to talk about it to me and not to ask her about it or try to see her.I waited a week and when i saw her out in her yard i stopped and tried to talk to her.She did not want to talk about it and asked me to leave.The first night of my experience was wonderful a life altering experience in a good way.The second night was very scary.Wish i could of controlled my fears .Always have wondered what i could have been privileged to experience.Did my nieghbor get the ride of a lifetime.Wish it could have been me.After my experience i developed severe headaches and a itchy rash behind my ear lobe on right side.Some small bumps developed behind right earlobe over time but never got bigger,still there today.This happened over28 years ago in july 1987 not long after 4th of july.But remember it like yesterday.Never told about this event except to some family and friends still not sure i should be speaking of it.Still have fears of who was involved and what it might invoke.
content.summary: First night was encounter with glowing orb at varying distance with closest proximity 10 feet or less.Second night encounter with entity closest proximity 20 to 30 feet at night

content.detailedDescription: Me and a friend where sitting in a park at night when i noticed a light slowly going across the sky, i pointed it out and commented that i thought is was a satellite. we semed to lose sight of it and then i once again saw another star-like light moving a lot faster than the "satellite" we had seen earlier. this light was moving one direction but seemed to be curving in another direction while still moving very fast. it slowed down and then my friend and i saw it eject or split into two fast moving lights, and they were also going opposite directions at a high speed. the two objects seemed to be the same size as far as i could tell which just opens further questions. as they sped in opposite directions they also started to fade into the night sky and then they were gone. it was during a festival and there were a lot of other people sitting in the park but me and my friend seemed to be the only ones who saw it. later that night i told another friend who wasn't with me during the sighting and he said he had also seen a bright light moving at high speed, but did not witness it split into two like the object i had seen.
content.summary: A bright light splitting into two bright lights and then going opposite directions

content.detailedDescription:
I was snowed in at a hotel on i40 in albuquerque,  new mexico heading west towards my home in las vegas, nevada, and i stepped outside my room and just started snapping pictures of the snow fall with my cell phone camera. i came back inside my room,and viewed my photos and noticed strange blue lights in a tree located in the parking lot in one of the pictures. i became excited and showed my daughter. i quickly went back outside but couldn't see the object in the tree anymore. 
 the next day i walked outside and looked at the same tree and there was nothing in the area that could have been a reasonable source for the presence of the blue lights in the photo.  i thought the object looked like a creature.
content.summary: Blue like positioned in a hotel parking tree with unknown source.

content.detailedDescription:
I was driving home around midnight on route one in wisscassett, maine and noticed a large (size of a bus? tractor trailer?) glowing ball of light in my rearview mirror about a half mile to a mile back on the road. could've been a regular vehicle somehow, but i've never seen that kind of large ball-ish glow from a car/truck/vehicle before. unlike regular vehicles at night which have two obvious glowing lights - the headlights - the light had no distinguishing source. it was just a large ball of light traveling very low to the road.

whatever it was, i was glad when it didn't catch-up to my car, and glad when it went away and/or i could no longer see it behind me.I'm reporting it in hopes that someone has an explanation and/or saw it, too.
content.summary: Large white glowing ball

content.detailedDescription: Going back to the summer of 2009,in st pauls cray, orpington. it was a nice sunny day, with the odd cloud about, i was sitting in the back garden with my partner having a glass of coke. i was looking up at the sky as normal, watching the high flying airliners, which were coming from the east, i then clocked this plane coming out of the murky blue sky from the north, it looked very large as it slowly came towards us. i then noticed that it did not have any engines under the wings, the near it got to us i could see that this plane was not a plane at all, it was a symmetrical cross, i then heard the sound of engines ,but the noise was coming from a plane, coming from the east, and to my amazement the plane went under the cross, this is when i realize how high this thing was. the cross was about four times the size of the airliner and it was much higher, by this time it was right above us, it was white to grey in colour, had no marking or engines, the end of the wings were curved and where the four wings joined in the middle, this to was curved, it was dead smooth all over, and it made no noise, by this time a cloud had come along obscuring the view of the cross we waited for it to come out of the cloud but we never saw it again. now i have also made a discovery that has been hidden for over 42 years by nasa and carl sagan which i can prove and no english news paper will print please look at the nasa photo i have sent, i know about all the small detail about this photo.
content.summary: it was a very large symmetrical cross, slowly flying from the north

that was the first timeive seen them one time since but was not as dramatic as the first time but no less as amazing.I would have never noticed them because theyre are so far up there and look like stars and are very hard to see and someone might mistake them for space junk or a satlelite but they travel in straight lines but curve slightly when theyre turning. so look up and watch u might see a moving star. they weree too far up to see them on my camera.
